sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM users 
WHERE user_id NOT IN (
    SELECT user_id 
    FROM comments
);

external_knowledge:
- "fair bit of attention" refers to videos that have received significant engagement;
- More than a dozen discussions means at least 10 comments;
- "how many days ago" refers to the number of days since upload.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT u.user_id, u.username
FROM users u
JOIN comments c ON u.user_id = c.user_id;

SELECT title, description
FROM videos
WHERE view_count = (SELECT MAX(view_count) FROM videos);

SELECT AVG(sentiment_score) AS average_sentiment_score
FROM sentiment_analysis
WHERE sentiment_score > 0.7;

SELECT DISTINCT users.username
FROM users
INNER JOIN comments ON users.user_id = comments.user_id;
